<doc id="897857" wikidata="Q7337383" url="?curid=897857" title="River Eden">
<text>River Eden may refer to:

==United Kingdom==
===England===
* River Eden, Cumbria
* River Eden, Kent

===Scotland===
* River Eden, Fife
* Eden Water, a tributary of the River Tweed

===Wales===
* Afon Eden, Gwynedd

==Elsewhere==
* Eden River (Dominica)

